description:

title: Valve Releases Proton 8.0-5 with HDR Support for Multiple Video Games
description:
Proton 8.0-5 compatibility tool for Steam Play is out with HDR support for several games on compatible hardware, including Steam Deck OLED, as well as support for new games.
